>> title: Crispy Cauliflower Rice Bowl
>> cuisine: Asian
>> tags: bowl, quick-assembly, vegan, soy-free
>> servings: 1

-- Assembly time: 5 minutes (plus 5 min reheat for cauliflower)

Add @../components/grains/coconut-basmati-rice{1%cup} as base in #bowl{}.

Reheat @../components/proteins/crispy-sesame-cauliflower{1%cup} in oven ~{5%minutes} to re-crisp.

Add crispy cauliflower to bowl.

Add @../components/vegetables/stir-fry-vegetable-mix{1/2%cup} (quick saute) or @../components/vegetables/curry-roasted-vegetables{1/2%cup}.

Drizzle @../components/sauces/ginger-sesame-dressing{2%tbsp} over top.

Top with @sesame seeds{1%tsp} and @green onions{2%tbsp}(sliced).

-- Crispy, saucy, and totally satisfying
